ZH: 等一下，我正在忙着。
EN: Wait a moment, I'm busy right now.

ZH: 给我一点时间，稍候再联系你。
EN: Give me some time, I'll reach out to you later.

ZH: 可以稍候一下吗？
EN: Can you wait a little bit?

ZH: 请稍候，我正在查找信息。
EN: Please hold on, I'm looking up information.

ZH: 老师稍候就会到教室来。
EN: The teacher will arrive in the classroom shortly.

ZH: 耐心稍候，厨师正在烹饪美食。
EN: Be patient, the chef is cooking delicious food.

ZH: 他说他稍候就会返回的。
EN: He said he will be back soon.

ZH: 请稍候，我正在处理其他客户的需求。
EN: Please hang on, I'm dealing with other clients' needs.

ZH: 我稍候会询问老板你的请求。
EN: I will ask the boss about your request when I get the chance.

ZH: 警察稍候就会到达事发现场。
EN: The police will arrive at the crime scene shortly.

ZH: 稍候，请保持电话通畅。
EN: Hold on, please keep the phone line open.

ZH: 请稍候，有人在投诉中。
EN: Please wait, someone is in the middle of making a complaint.

ZH: 我们需要稍候才能得到答复。
EN: We need to wait a little bit to get a response.

ZH: 车子稍候就会到达目的地。
EN: The car will arrive at the destination shortly.

ZH: 请稍候，我需要一些时间来思考。
EN: Please wait, I need some time to think.

ZH: 你可以稍候一会吗？
EN: Can you wait for a while?

ZH: 稍候将会有新的通知发布。
EN: There will be new announcements published shortly.

ZH: 耐心稍候，机场巴士马上就会到达。
EN: Be patient, the airport bus will arrive soon.

ZH: 请稍候，我将很快回复你的邮件。
EN: Please wait, I will reply to your email very soon.

ZH: 我们稍候就会开始会议。
EN: We will begin the meeting shortly.
